description:
This course will show you some great linkbuilding ideas you can use 1:1 on your own projects or adapt them a little. These linkbuilding ideas are generally not known and if you do all of them then the possibility of ranking higher than your competitors is very high.

Each tip is a short clip of what it's about and how you can practically copy it or adapt it for your own purposes.

I know it's sometimes hard to come up with good ideas to do linkbuilding. The worst thing to do is use blackhat tactics. By going through my course you will see how whitehat tactics can be used to increase rankings and to give your SEO efforts a kickstart!

Happy Linkbuilding!
title: Awesome linkbuilding ideas to outsmart your Competition!
